popular_videos.video_title: HOW TO MAKE GIANT SLIME GOO Easy Science Experiment for kids!
popular_videos.video_description:
GIANT SLIME IN KIDDLE POOL FUN! In this video Ryan and his family will show you how to make slime (ooze) using household ingredients  that you can do at home! This science experiment is so easy and fun not only for kids, but fun for the whole family! 

What you'll need: (Super easy)
1.) 1 teaspoon of Borax ( can find at any grocery store or Walmart near the laundry detergent) mix with 1 cup of water
2.) Mix a bottle of 4oz glue with 1/2 cup of water in a separate container
3.) Add food coloring to the glue solution
4.) Mix solution with borax and solution with glue together
5.) use your hand and knee the slime 
6.)Drain our the extra water into the sink
7.) Can be store in the fridge to last longer!!!
8.) Have fun and let us know how your slime turn out!

recommended_videos.title: HOW TO MAKE GIANT SLIME GOO Easy Science Experiment for kids!
recommended_videos.description:
GIANT SLIME IN KIDDLE POOL FUN! In this video Ryan and his family will show you how to make slime (ooze) using household ingredients  that you can do at home! This science experiment is so easy and fun not only for kids, but fun for the whole family! 

What you'll need: (Super easy)
1.) 1 teaspoon of Borax ( can find at any grocery store or Walmart near the laundry detergent) mix with 1 cup of water
2.) Mix a bottle of 4oz glue with 1/2 cup of water in a separate container
3.) Add food coloring to the glue solution
4.) Mix solution with borax and solution with glue together
5.) use your hand and knee the slime 
6.)Drain our the extra water into the sink
7.) Can be store in the fridge to last longer!!!
8.) Have fun and let us know how your slime turn out!
